{"id":232555,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/贺卫方-胡适文物图片展/","date":"2012-06-18T08:30:50Z","modified":"2012-06-18T08:30:50Z","title":"贺卫方 | 胡适文物图片展","content":"<p><p>胡适文物图片展</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s14.sinaimg.cn/orignal/488663204c2babf61c2ad\"><img src=\"http://s14.sinaimg.cn/middle/488663204c2babf61c2ad&#038;690\" name=\"image_operate_59171340007746534\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n今天，参加毕业生合影后，路过北大图书馆，远远看到门厅上有“胡适文物图片展”的字样，就转道进了图书馆，遇到特藏部张红扬主任。我过去曾承她帮助，看了馆内的胡适藏书以及胡颂平日记原件。她热情邀请我参与了今天的开展仪式。展览上，看到不少以前未见的胡适照片，还有一些北大馆所藏胡适著作，多为有胡适手迹的初刊本。值得向有兴趣的朋友们推荐。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s2.sinaimg.cn/orignal/48866320079df7a7a26f1\"><img src=\"http://s2.sinaimg.cn/middle/48866320079df7a7a26f1&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s6.sinaimg.cn/orignal/488663204c2bacc464515\"><img src=\"http://s6.sinaimg.cn/middle/488663204c2bacc464515&#038;690\" name=\"image_operate_32311340007802740\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s2.sinaimg.cn/orignal/488663204c2bad0d3f9c1\"><img src=\"http://s2.sinaimg.cn/middle/488663204c2bad0d3f9c1&#038;690\" /><br />\n</a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://s6.sinaimg.cn/orignal/488663204c2bad4cbae95\"><img src=\"http://s6.sinaimg.cn/middle/488663204c2bad4cbae95&#038;690\" name=\"image_operate_96881340007730227\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img width=\"34\" height=\"17\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/9ce382f81265.gif.gif\" />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469641,474922&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473458&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.weibo.com/tag/%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F\">青春就应该这样绽放</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http: